{"tid":1339436,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"對付元朗方法No. 1","createTime":"2019-07-21T15:16:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T15:16:51.000Z","uid":116545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"43ee3002580ec60fb084313c1dd42be515febd19","tid":1339436,"uid":116545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:16:52.000Z","msg":"大家都知到元朗有好多村屋，寮屋<br />\n<br />\n<strong>村屋</strong>可能會有僭建物，如果唔sure都可以去 屋字署 問下，<span style=\"color: red;\">記得用email同fax寄出你地既查詢</span><br />\n<br />\n聯略方法：<br />\n屋宇署<br />\n樓宇 (1) 部<br />\n村屋組<br />\n地址 九龍油麻地海庭道11號西九龍政府合署北座屋宇署總部<br />\n傳真 3168 2039<br />\n<br />\n背景資料：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bd.gov.hk/tc/safety-inspection/ubw/learn-more-about-UBW/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bd.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fsafety-inspection%2Fubw%2Flearn-more-about-UBW%2Findex.html&d=gWuinA8KpjkBZIRqFxHaGs04bh6pArHnk2fwDmvpgUU%3D&h=60a4968a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bd.gov.hk/tc/safety-inspection/ubw/learn-more-about-UBW/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n寮屋，港英政府係1982年做了一次squatter survey，每一間比一個number，<br />\n只要唔拆，唔改變用途，Keep住原有的建築材料，就係合法。<br />\n但只要拆過or改變用途or改變建築材料or僭建就會違法。<br />\n如果唔sure就去 地政總署 問下，<span style=\"color: red;\">記得用email同fax寄出你地既查詢</span><br />\n<br />\n聯略方法：<br />\n地政總署<br />\n地政處<br />\n寮屋管制小組<br />\n地址 香港北角渣華道333號北角政府合署13樓<br />\n辦公室電話 2231 3044<br />\n傳真 2116 9018<br />\n<br />\n背景資料：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.landsd.gov.hk/tc/squatter_control/sqctrl.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.landsd.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fsquatter_control%2Fsqctrl.htm&d=gWuinA8KpjkBZIRqFxHaGs04bh6pArHnk2fwDmvpgUU%3D&h=197d17cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.landsd.gov.hk/tc/squatter_control/sqctrl.htm</a>"}]}